<h2>Local KHRD Help: Person</h2>

<p>The yggdrasil "person" entity corresponds to a KHRD legacy userid i.e. AAAA999 (the associated Matricle event contains this legacy body/person identifier.</p>
<p>Preloaded persons from legacy data have identifiers starting from 10000. Persons added locally have numbers starting from 1.</p>
<p>Please note:</p>
<ul>
<li>only NAMES are provided;</li>
<li>dates and locations of birth/death are derived from the events associated with this person;</li>
</ul>

<p>There is no provision as yet for structured/validated data capture about persons.</p>

